# Quantum entropy seed -- PRIVATE BUILD SECRET. The raw bytes must never be
# committed or published: a canary-fold constant only helps if it stays off
# the public record. tools/quantum/qrng_seed.py + requirements.txt ARE tracked
# so anyone can regenerate their own; the bytes are not. build/qrng_seed.inc is
# already covered by build/ above.
tools/quantum/seed.bin
tools/quantum/seed.inc
tools/quantum/qrng_manifest.txt
src/include/qrng_seed.inc
